ONLYOFFICE Docs Pterodactyl packaging
=====================================

This directory contains build, installation, runtime, and Pterodactyl packaging
for ONLYOFFICE Docs (also known as ONLYOFFICE DocumentServer).

ONLYOFFICE DocumentServer is developed by Ascensio System SIA and contributors.
It is distributed under the GNU Affero General Public License version 3. A copy
of that license is provided in LICENSE-AGPL-3.0.

Upstream project and corresponding source:
https://github.com/ONLYOFFICE/DocumentServer

Upstream container build source:
https://github.com/ONLYOFFICE/Docker-DocumentServer

Source for this Pterodactyl packaging and its container modifications:
https://github.com/CKATEPTb/dockerfiles/tree/master/onlyoffice/documents

The custom image is assembled from the upstream ONLYOFFICE DocumentServer image.
